Select genes that are expressed above a treshold of counts exp and in at least n replicates

"geneSelect" <- function(cnt,splt,exp=1,nrep=2){
  rowSums(sapply(lapply(
    split.data.frame(t(cnt >= exp),splt)
    ,colSums), ">=", nrep)) >= 1
}
